collections::binary_heap::BinaryHeap::<T.doc:
Returns the length of the binary heap.

# Examples

Basic usage:

```
use std::collections::BinaryHeap;
let heap = BinaryHeap::from([1, 3]);

assert_eq!(heap.len(), 2);
```

